{"tid":1187712,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"梁美芬：律師會立場書來得太遲，宜家先講域外法權？下次唔該早啲","createTime":"2019-06-06T00:02:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-06T01:20:02.000Z","uid":41243,"like":1,"dislike":45,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b292d3ca1eec6701e72b40e744c71c799c12b312","tid":1187712,"uid":41243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T00:02:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/RTHKVNEWS/videos/2315429588722148/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FRTHKVNEWS%2Fvideos%2F2315429588722148%2F&d=HGsIALD6rBmJFWdd%2FklEli3IRifvRw8PV%2BxDOhj55DY%3D&h=f87020e8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/RTHKVNEWS/videos/2315429588722148/</a><br />\n<br />\n【梁美芬：律師會立場書來得太遲難發揮作用】 <br />\n<br />\n律師會就修訂《逃犯條例》發表立場書，建議擴大本港法院域外法權，處理包括謀殺和誤殺等嚴重罪行。 <br />\n<br />\n經民聯梁美芬說，律師會的立場書太遲公布，意見難以發揮作用。她指，政府已作兩次重大讓步，包括加入公平審訊等人權保障，法庭審訊時，亦可考慮政府啟動時有否提出有關措施，她對律師會的立場書不夠聚焦最新情況，感到可惜。"},{"pid":"385b673d9041b2552d48ea1a4c46c634b5800660","tid":1187712,"uid":57677,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T00:05:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q1fbUKP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ1fbUKP.jpg&h=ac5e6f98&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b2c2b0a231628a10e2aaa1a2130b923fde7c11bd","tid":1187712,"uid":159448,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T00:07:15.000Z","msg":"其實佢都唔想立法 真心話佢地遲左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"913b84881248d5f243ab1db615c632d420c0315b","tid":1187712,"uid":33307,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T00:11:35.000Z","msg":"遲左？即係冇講錯？"},{"pid":"c1dab6ec5d488a7bfc35a642f056cbb776176aca","tid":1187712,"uid":99962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T00:13:12.000Z","msg":"想香港快啲死姐"},{"pid":"aee511c9b5421690194736fce5ba1026ede10f1d","tid":1187712,"uid":53278,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201